Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda/realtek - Rewrite ALC880 model=uniwill-dig with auto-parser
Git-commit: 967b88c47744f7ec424c71630c1f551d34e08eef
Patch-mainline: 3.4-rc3
References: FATE#314311

ALC880 model=uniwill-dig requires the fix-up of bogus BIOS pin default
configurations.  Other than that, it's pretty normal.

Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

